name: Unmasked 03
description: My concept is inspired by the incredible resilience of BIPOC women and non-binary folks. It is one thing to survive in this life with one marginalized identity, to do it with multiple is a damn superpower. I understand this struggle as a Colombian-American woman. The blood sweat and tears of our ancestors have gotten us here. I want this design to ooze a quiet confidence and internal strength. An essence that can only grow inside someone through the collective resilience of their forebears.
